title: Nollywood Actress, Kate Henshaw Is Looking Stunning In New Photos
summary:
Kate Henshaw Veteran Nollywood actress, Kate Henshaw, who in 2008, won the Africa Movie Academy Award for Best Actress in a Leading Role, has taken to her Instagram page to share some stunning photos of herself.
She flaunted her hand bag which had the colours of the Nigerian flag.
The 47 year old was one of the guests invited to an event by media mogul, Debola Lagos.
meta_description: Online portal that provide breaking news and updates in Nigeria
text:
Kate Henshaw

Veteran Nollywood actress, Kate Henshaw, who in 2008, won the Africa Movie Academy Award for Best Actress in a Leading Role, has taken to her Instagram page to share some stunning photos of herself.

She flaunted her hand bag which had the colours of the Nigerian flag. The 47 year old was one of the guests invited to an event by media mogul, Debola Lagos.
